:

1. *Ljubav* je najbolja stvar na svetu. (Love is the best thing in the world.)
2. Volim te i uvek ću te *ljubiti*. (I love you and I will always love you.)
3. Ona mu je govorila da je *ljubav* najvažnija. (She was telling him that love is the most important.)
4. Oni su se *ljubili* na obali mora. (They were kissing on the shore.)
5. Osećam da ću te *ljubiti* zauvek. (I feel that I will love you forever.)